utils.actions

Annotation Type SessionAuth


  • @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Target(value={METHOD,TYPE})
 @Inherited
 @Documented
public @interface SessionAuth
    Annotation Interface which binds the request intercepter Action SessionAuthAction to every controller method which is annotated with SessionAuth. Verifying session based login and the users permissions.
